node.text:
Thank you, everyone, for your endless love and support over the last couple of days 💕 I’m not gonna lie, this virus is kicking my ass. I will keep everyone updated along with the info I've learned to combat some symptoms along the way. Swipe up in my stories to check out some #covid_19 resources. Be careful out there, if I wasn't  vaccinated I'm sure I would have been in the hospital by now. My best piece of advice, no matter what your state or local government might say, limit interactions between vaccinated and unvaccinated people, without wearing a mask; especially in places where you work out. This sh*t is as real as it's gets! Stay safe! #covid #msbarbarak

#covidvacccine #covid #barbarakavovit #deltavariant #healthiswealth #nyc

node.text:
Well, I have #Covid, down for the count, and I’m fully vaccinated. This delta variant is REAL and it begs the question, what do we do next? How do we get people vaccinated, and continue the testing to avoid this unnecessary spread. I'm so thankful that I AM vaccinated, it will definitely help with the severity of the symptoms and spreading the virus; due to the viral load in my body. But if more people got vaccinated, individuals would not be contracting the virus. Health should NOT be political - masks work. Continue to wear them in crowded places, protect yourself and the people around you. I will keep ya'll updated on my symptoms and quarantine plans. All my love, 

Barbara K 
💙💙👠🔨

.
.
#msbarbarak #covid_19 #covidvacccine #health #barbarakavovit #nyc
